<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV93">
<l>curumparaṅku taṇṭuḻāytu taintalarnta pātamē</l>
<l>virumpiniṉṟi ṟaiñcuvēṟki raṅkaraṅka vāṇaṉē</l>
<l>karumpirunta kaṭṭiyēka ṭaṟkiṭanta kaṇṇaṉē</l>
<l>yirumparaṅka veñcarantu rantavilli rāmaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who dwell in Raṅgam, show grace to me, who remain begging with desire for</l>
<l>[Your] feet that bloom, being pressed by cool tulasi pierced by bees!</l>
<l>O rock-candy made of sugarcane! O Kṛṣṇa who lies on the ocean!</l>
<l>O Rāma, archer who shot cruel arrows so that steel[-like Rakshasas] were pierced!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
